data.text:
About

Filipina broadcaster and politician who served as the Member of the House of Representatives for Las Pi√±as. She previously served as Chief Operating Officer of Brittany Corporation. She was the youngest person to ever hold the position.

Before Fame

She studied business management at Ateneo de Manila University.

Trivia

She was a co-host of Wil Time Bigtime from 2012 to 2013. She also co-hosted Wowowillie.

Family Life

In 2012, she married Erwin Genuino. They have a son named Tristan Emmanuel. Her father is the former President of the Senate Manuel Villar and her mother is Senator Cynthia Villar.
